description: AMUNDI ETF GOVIES 0-6 MONTHS EURO INVESTMENT GRADE UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the FTSE Eurozone Government Bill 0-6 Month Capped Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This index measures the performance of short-term sovereign bonds of certain Eurozone States with a maturity between 0-6 months. Please refer to the fund prospectus for more details on the index rules.
name: Amundi ETF Govies 0-6 Months Euro Investment Grade UCITS ETF DR
